OL,6,FRevelations around police surveillance
OL,7,Fof two journalists in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fare just the tip of a "very large and
OL,9,Fvery dangerous iceberg", one of the
OL,10,Freporters has warned.JBarry McCaffrey
OL,11,Fwas commenting as campaigners called
OL,12,Ffor the Policing Board to set up an
OL,13,Finquiry into allegations of unlawful
OL,14,Fcovert surveillance of journalists in
OL,15,Fthe region.JAmnesty International and
OL,16,Fthe Committee on the Administration of
OL,17,FJustice (CAJ) have written to the
OL,18,Fboard, the oversight body for the
OL,19,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,20,F(PSNI), raising "serious concerns over
OL,21,Fhow widespread the practice of
OL,22,Fsurveillance of journalists and others
OL,23,Fmay have been".
