OL,6,FThe move comes after a tribunal was
OL,7,Ftold that police mounted a covert
OL,8,Fsurveillance operation following the
OL,9,Farrest of Mr McCaffrey and his
OL,10,Fcolleague Trevor Birney in a bid to
OL,11,Funmask one of their sources.JThe
OL,12,FInvestigatory Powers Tribunal (IPT)
OL,13,Fwas told last week that the arrest of
OL,14,Ffilm-makers in 2018 was a "disruptive"
OL,15,Ftactic to see if the reporters would
OL,16,Freach out to the source after their
OL,17,Frelease from custody.JThe tribunal is
OL,18,Falso investigating several incidents,
OL,19,Fthe first dating back to 2011,
OL,20,Finvolving police accessing Mr
OL,21,FMcCaffrey's phone data.JThe PSNI and
OL,22,FMetropolitan Police in London both
OL,23,Fobtained the reporter's phone data
OL,24,Fwithout his knowledge or consent.JIn
